<br>
What worked for me was to pull him out of the building.  I got myself a shrink potion to make pulling easier.  With a good magic and fire save the spells he cast while following me didnt hurt too much.  When I got out the door I jump into the water and swim to the shore past the priest of discord, basicly between the waterfall and the area where the ceiling drops.  There is plenty of room there to fight, this gives you room to chain pet if you have to, and keeps you out of range of his AE spells.  I was able to single pull him out of the room and past all the other gnomers and gnomebots.  I have not tried it solo yet, but did it duo with myself and another mage.<br>
<br>
Just sharing the info I saw first hand, I dont know what others will find works for them, but this is what worked for me. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><br>
